editorialNotes.standard: HealthifyMe will change the way you look at weight loss and training. Plus, HealthifyMe has over 1,000 fun activities to add to workout routines (including a yoga instructor). Now you can set goals, monitor your progress and slim down at your own pace. Backed by some of India’s top health experts, HealthifyMe has given us the confidence to get our fitness journey started.
